sources.title: Mask of Thorn | Full Movie | Mystery Horror | Martin w. Payne
sources.description:
Mask of Thorn - Bethany Lovell has struggled to fit in her whole life. Between overbearing parents and her odd behaviour she has always felt like she was on the outside. That is until Avondale's popular clique kidnap her for a surprise birthday party to celebrate her sweet sixteen. What they don't realise is that Bethany is now the target of the urban legend     known as 'Thorn' and tonight he has returned for her and nothing will stand in his way, as the Bloodletting Behemoth cuts his way through the small town in search of his latest victim and only one person can stop him.
2019.  Stars: Eve Kathryn Oliver, Sophie Bryant, Maria Lee Metheringham
